  "body": "<h1 style=\"font-weight: 800; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">PvP Pure</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2em auto;\">\n  A sleek black-and-white resource pack enhancing Minecraft’s GUI and items with minimalist elegance.\n</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">🛠️ Features</h2>\n<ul style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2em auto; padding-left: 1.2em;\">\n  <li>GUI upgrade</li>\n  <li>Textures: GUI, blocks, and items</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">🎨 Style</h2>\n<p style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2em auto;\">\n  Black and white GUI and item textures with a clean, minimalist aesthetic.<br />\n  Many textures are reused or adapted from <strong>Elektrofy</strong>.\n</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.3em;\">📝 Version</h2>\n<p style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2em auto;\">\n  <strong>Current Version:</strong> <code>0.5</code> <em>(Beta)</em>\n</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.3em;\">📄 Requirements</h2>\n<p style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 0.5em auto;\">\n  No mods required to use this pack.\n</p>\n<p style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2em auto;\">\n  <strong>Optional:</strong> For a full UI experience, we recommend the\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/polytone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"font-weight: 600; color: #0077cc; text-decoration: none;\">Polytone</a>.\n</p>\n\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 3em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; text-align: center; font-weight: 900;\">➕ Other Projects</h2>\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;\">\n  <tr>\n\t<td style=\"padding: 1em; width: 140px; height: 160px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">\n      <div style=\"font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><strong>Essentials Style</div>\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/essentials-style\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/8zAhdB4V/f73795cb02b0e975192d6a2492717ea70c99459d.png\" alt=\"Essentials Style\" width=\"96\" style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto;\" />\n      </a>\n    </td>\n    <td style=\"padding: 1em; width: 140px; height: 160px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">\n      <div style=\"font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><strong>Elektrofy</div>\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/elektofy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/GtitqdU9/4faccf78251915c584bb732f241bf4609c9c2060.png\" alt=\"Elektrofy Pack\" width=\"96\" style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto;\" />\n      </a>\n    </td>\n    <td style=\"padding: 1em; width: 140px; height: 160px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">\n      <div style=\"font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><strong>Suitcase Totem</div>\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/suitcase-totem\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/Gj6Bdchj/5d4173991e87a5d4ef2949455c8ed5132335d5c2_96.webp\" alt=\"Suitcase Totem\" width=\"96\" style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto;\" />\n      </a>\n    </td>\n    <td style=\"padding: 1em; width: 140px; height: 160px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">\n      <div style=\"font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><strong>Shulker Totem</div>\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/shulker-totem\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/eDU7SXE3/6a629ae0b030dd573483b608e467d873fec71120_96.webp\" alt=\"Shulker Totem\" width=\"96\" style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto;\" />\n      </a>\n    </td>\n    <td style=\"padding: 1em; width: 140px; height: 160px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;\">\n      <div style=\"font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><strong>Monkke</div>\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/monkke\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/kyrPHvY8/45cea89f7fb8188942b8761dfe780864e38b6fd2.png\" alt=\"Monkke\" width=\"96\" style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto;\" />\n      </a>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic; margin-top: 2em; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n  More visual packs and enhancements coming soon!\n</p>",
